channel.title: My No-Ip address is not working
channel.description: Hello everyone, I'm in need of some help. My No-Ip address is not working, I portforwarded, i tried EVERYTHING. I ran my client, and i had everything turned on for my no-ip, but it says "error connecting to server" Somone help? I made an exception in my firewall and everything. I'm using windows 7, (i also tried it on my other computer with windows 98) and it still did not work! help me somoene. Thank you!=) Please help?
